> *"Honestly and brutally, there was nothing better we could have done."*

 - Anker Jørgensen, 2007

This is a game of alternate history. While historical accuracy is a major concern, keep in mind that this is a game, and that any divergence from actual events will necessarily have to involve some element of make-believe. Nevertheless, please let the author know if there are any glaring mistakes.

This game was made as a total conversion mod of Automn Chens amazing 'Social Democracy: An alternative History' game which I'd also recommend you try out.

For more information on the politics and government of Denmark during the period, see the "Library" page on the top left. If this is your first time playing the game, it is strongly recommended that you read at least some of this information.

